The Company has a Business Continuity Policy (BCP). The main objective of BCP is to maintain business continuity under disruptive incidents with an aim to minimize impact on:
•	Human life and other living beings;
•	Environment and related eco-systems;
•	Economic losses;
•	All stakeholders (such as investors, employees).

To make this BCP more robust, the Company plans training and awareness sessions across the mines and plant locations. Apart from training, BCP testing is done periodically to check its efficacy and improve it further based on the gaps observed during testing.
